            </p>
            <p>Data stored by these cookies never show personal details from which your inidual identity can be established.If you disable or opt-out of these cookies, you may not be able to use certain features of our websites and services, and it may reduce the support or information that we can provide you.</p>
            <p>
              (c) Preferences Cookies.
              These cookies allow our site to remember the choices you have made about your preferences, such as what language you prefer, or what your user name and password are so that you can automatically log in and we can provide you with better services and improve our shopping experience. If you reject these cookies, you may feel that the efficiency of owsing the web has decreased.
